          <span>Launch $5/mo Premium Tier (Stripe)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="icon-[tabler--clock] text-warning"></span>
          <span>Add private audio posts (Supabase Storage)</span>
        </li>
        <li class="flex items-center gap-2">
          <span class="icon-[tabler--clock] text-warning"></span>
