  </div>
  <div id="tabs-roadmap-phase4-content" class="hidden" role="tabpanel" aria-labelledby="tabs-roadmap-phase4">
    <div class="space-y-4">
      <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold">Scale & Sustain (Months 6-12)</h3>
